3/ |accessdate=June 1, 2019 |work=IndieWire |date=March 6, 2019 |language=en}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| [[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Variety Special (Live)|Outstanding Variety Special (Live)]]\n| ''[[72nd Tony Awards]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite news |last1=Travers |first1=Ben |title=2019 Emmy Predictions: The 71st Annual Primetime Emmys Are Gonna be Wild |url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/03/2019-emmy-predictions-71-primetime-emmys-nominations-winners-1202048893/ |accessdate=June 1, 2019 |work=IndieWire |date=March 6, 2019 |language=en}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| rowspan=3|2020\n| [[62nd Annual Grammy Awards|Grammy Awards]]\n| [[Grammy Award for Best American Roots Performance|Best American Roots Performance]]\n| \"Saint Honesty\"\n| {{won}}\n|{{center|<ref>{{cite web|title=2020 Grammy Nominees|website=grammy.com|accessdate=November 20, 2019|url=https://www.grammy.com/grammys/news/2020-grammy-awards-complete-nominees-list|year=2020}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| rowspan=2|[[2020 Laurence Olivier Awards|Olivier Awards]]\n| [[Laurence Olivier Award for Outstanding Achievement in Music|Best Original Score or New Orchestrations]]\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''[[Waitress (musical)|Waitress]]''\n| {{pending}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web|title=Olivier Awards 2020|website=Official London Theatre|accessdate=March 4, 2020|url=https://officiallondontheatre.com/olivier-awards/year/olivier-awards-2020|year=2020}}</ref>}}\n|-\n| [[Laurence Olivier Award for Best New Musical|Best New Musical]]\n| {{pending}}\n| {{center|<ref>{{cite web|title=Olivier Awards 2020|website=Official London Theatre|accessdate=March 4, 2020|url=https://officiallondontheatre.com/olivier-awards/year/olivier-awards-2020|year=2020}}</ref>}}\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|colwidth=30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{sisterlinks|d=Q230445|n=no|wikt=no|b=no|v=no|voy=no|species=no|m=no|mw=no|commons=Category:Sara Bareilles|s=no}}\n{{Wikipedia books}}\n* {{Official website}}\n* {{Curlie|Arts/Music/Bands_and_Artists/B/Bareilles%2C_Sara